{
  "stem": "25831.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We went on exercises near the city to shoot down Polish planes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was always-- we were so close to the Polish border.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were taught, you know, how to lie down without being seen and keep our heels down when we lie down.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I enjoyed that a lot.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was the only Jew.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I don't think anybody paid any attention to the fact that-- because, after all, they thought that if we are attacked by the Poles, I would suffer as much as they do.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, one teacher was a wonderful man who had enough courage to say to one of the kids who already came dressed in the Hitler Youth shirt, and he didn't know the answer to a certain question, and he says why don't you become a stable boy for Hitler instead of coming to school?",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You're wasting your time.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In other words, there was not enough fear yet, you know, for a teacher to make a remark like this.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This was in 1933.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At that time I was in a gymnasium, which is the equivalent of high school here.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I started that at age 9 and 3/4.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I left the school three years because before the official graduation in order to get a graduation certificate from another school, a commercial high school, which would entitle me to enter a university and get a degree, a PhD.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Everything was PhD.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't think they had master's degrees in business administration and commerce economics and so on.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] but the last-- I stayed in my first school until 1934.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, there were rallies.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Berlin was a much more liberal city.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Berlin had the greatest number of drama critics, Jews, film directors.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
